      "citation": "Ps 80:2-3, 15-16, 18-19, R. v.4\nLord, make us turn to you;\nlet us see your face and we shall be saved.",
      "summary": "",
      "antiphon": "Ps 80:2-3, 15-16, 18-19, R. v.4\nLord, make us turn to you;\nlet us see your face and we shall be saved."
    },
    {
      "type": "second",
      "citation": "1 Cor 1:3-9",
      "summary": "The Lord will strengthen us to the end."
    },
    {
      "type": "gospel_verse",
      "citation": "cf. Ps 85:8",
      "summary": "Lord, show us your love; and grant us your salvation."
    },
    {
