      "option": 1,
      "citation": "Cf. Ps 25 (24):1–3",
      "text": "To you, I lift up my soul, O my God.\nIn you, I have trusted; let me not be put to shame.\nNor let my enemies exult over me; and let none who hope in you be put to shame."
    },
